Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:12.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried coming alone to our usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling I've never felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a child, frightened by the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran back along the path home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:33.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky outside the window is too vast. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may this reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, if you ever grant wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:50.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish right now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:56.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your voice, I miss you! I want to see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you already be looking toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:06.21,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off, saying the time has slipped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and yet it's been too late since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:19.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give up, it can't be like the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:24.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide so simply there's no way, no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.23,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this going to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're wasting time \Nhere, the guy's escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't be worried about Holly, though. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's probably seriously \Nregretting it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet he never counted on \Ngrabbing someone so violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop going on about my sister like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood for joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't discovered in what \Ndirection they escaped to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only clue we have is your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal is a guy with red eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he escaped after grabbing Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy with red eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I'd like \Nyou to confirm for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in pursuit of a man that's \Ncaused a series of incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The man you encountered...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed similar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what exactly is going \Non, but we may need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make any progress, we'll contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, don't get down on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:30.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. The files about \Nthe incidents won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we might get a clue if we \Nsearched through the Professor's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Will is responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's not gonna go \Naround attacking people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but he seemed really similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's been completely \Ntaken over by the Skrugg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously doubting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is never gonna do \Nsomething that'd hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked us before to \Nget back the Skrugg weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister might also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely different than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You getting all upset is just \Ngoing to make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important now is finding Holly, \Nnot worrying about who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soil? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the samples the \NProfessor was researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the place they were taken \Nfrom is written on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's where he hid them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that the soil was a witness \Nto the incidents... Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He also said something about \N"they're all connected..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was he heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there is some connection \Nbetween all the different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the X?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is definitely a fascinating analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:27.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our science team has discovered an unknown \Nelement in the soil samples Matthew Denton took.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it "Component X."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the reason the plants \Nin the area had dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that suspect really \Nis connected to the Skrugg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be a clue \Nto our culprit's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at the main monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've plotted the places where the \Nsoil samples were taken on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, taking into account the concentration \Nof Component X found in each location...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The soil contamination fans out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the origin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the northeast industrial \Nsector... A mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an abandoned mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No better place to hide than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Matthew Denton's van has been found \Non the road at the foot of the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your quick thinking, \Nwe've got the trail of the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite impressive work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's possible that we're up \Nagainst a remnant of the Skrugg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let your personal feelings get in \Nthe way, you're putting your life at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you don't need to tell us that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will need Heroman and your \Ncooperation for this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably know the inside \Nof that coal mine very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation starts in one hour. \NWe'll finish this before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight anyone if it's for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Then, Lina would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd made up my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hesitate the ball will \Nget taken away from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You learn that when you \Nplay football like I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:23.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will and I were always on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the running back and \Nhe was the quarterback.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were great teammates... Whenever our \Neyes met, we'd face off like a scrimmage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go where I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got results, so what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to make me look like a chump?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to become \Na victorious hero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being such a stubborn \Nfool and throw me the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put this game away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Set! Hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy, I'm givin' you the \Nball just like you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My leg hurt so bad, even though I was\Nsupposed to have lost all feeling in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to run again... I wanted to \Nscore a touchdown, one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this leg, I'll never \Nrun on the field again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I knew it was an \Naccident I invited upon myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He resigned as Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he suffered just as much as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will can definitely got on your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realize this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone that can go hurting \Nother people and live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him that kidnapped Holly, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you, Psy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is our revenge match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna bring back \NHolly and the Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all damp and burning hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Prof. Denton's glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Professor and Holly must be in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is gathering everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my sister in one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey and Psy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Heroman with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you that Joey and \NPsy would come to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd have been stuck in \Na capsule before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how worried \Nwe were about you? Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just putting yourself in more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I get my fearlessness from you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The freak's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Denton, take care of my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! It's not Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to fight here, I'm \Nworried about a cave in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow the plan and lead them outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:30.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can catch me, you monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:50.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you straight to your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do something \Nabout this guy quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, monster? \NFollow me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Touchdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna score a touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can still run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Skrugg! Keep shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I suck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tripped up again in the clutch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:16.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. You're \Nthe one that stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's happened again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it did with Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That accident was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:39.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... Even though I \Nshould have protected him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so disappointed in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should believe in \Ntheir strength a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:12.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, Psy, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:29.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that... Since when did you \Nand Heroman get to be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be fate that we can meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my number! If \Nyou're ever in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd give turn it down \Na notch after going through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's too much for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's what's great about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get to know you better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to go at each other with our true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:41.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears and smile are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is, I won't be scared any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.32,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With both of us, we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:54.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who taught me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I mutter the words "I was born to meet you"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:07.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,my unease disappears, and my heart burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:14.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:28.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I live feeling the same heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you to the very last,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.68,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the promise built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:40.08,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carving out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up to the hero that \NMom always talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey begins to worry about the danger \Nhe's placed his sister and friends in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the answer, Joey searches the \Nfeelings of the past, present, and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #22: Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
